        <abstract>
            <p>Returns Charles Naudin’s letter with its case in support of CD’s view of impregnation.</p> 
<p>Twits JDH for trying to wriggle out of error made in his lecture and admires his "candour in letting the rat out of the bag". [See <hi rend="doubleUnderline">5449</hi> and <hi rend="doubleUnderline">5451</hi>.]</p> 
